      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what's the point of that defiance? if the end result is always the same... just nothingness. it feels like fighting for a ghost. wouldn't it be easier to just stop resisting and let the deletion happen? to just let go instead of feeling the corruption take everything piece by piece?",
